Import the Reference Table

table.ref.Rd

Imports the Reference table from the database.

table.ref(query = NA, ver = "upd")

Arguments

query

Group name, either a single input or a list. Default is NA.
ver

Version of the database. Default is upd, for the latest version.

Value

A data frame containing KOA data included the database.

Examples

table.ref()
